<title>WHEN THE BEAUTIFUL GATES UNFOLD</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Zan leh thim nuoiah vakvai sawt ta puoi tiu,
 Kawtkhak hawih chuh hawn ahih tieng;
 Pathien vakna khawpi achun leng hitiu,
 Kawtkhak hawih chuh hawn ahih tieng.

[V2]
 Kawtkhak hawih chuh hawn ahih tieng,
 Kawtkhak hawih chuh hawn ahih tieng;
 I Lalpau chuh mui tingun kipak tai tiu,
 Kawtkhak hawih chuh hawn ahih tieng.

[V3]
 2. Kuong chawlhna mun ah hehpih te'n ei ngak ui,
 Kawtkhak hawih chuh hawn ahih tieng;
 Gitloh beihna tung ding eina lamtuoh di'n,
 Kawtkhak hawih chuh hawn ahih tieng.

[V4]
 3. Damloh, lungkham leh natna umta puo'n a,
 Kawtkhak hawih chuh hawn ahih tieng;
 Guol ngaih khensa tawh kipaka kiho ding,
 Kawtkhak hawih chuh hawn ahih tieng.

[V5]
 4. Kipahna genzawh senloh chuh chang ta'ng ka,
 Kawtkhak hawih chuh hawn ahih tieng;
 Ziechun Pathien thiengtho tak chuh mu ta'ng ka,
 Kawtkhak hawih chuh hawn ahih tieng.

[V6]
 5. Lopina vak chun-ei um kimvel tan a,
 Kawtkhak hawih chuh hawn ahih tieng;
 Luigal akhun kipak takin la sai tiu,
 Kawtkhak hawih chuh hawn ahih tieng.

[V7]
 6. Damsung puokgik in ei subuoi ta puo'n a,
 Kawtkhak hawih chuh hawn ahih tieng;
 Kipak tawp loin Krista tawh cheng khawm tai tiu,
 Kawtkhak hawih chuh hawn</lyrics>
</song>